      <h2 id="proxmox-hosts" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">2.5 Proxmox Hypervisor Hosts (192.168.1.x) - Virtualization Layer</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
        <strong>Purpose:</strong> Proxmox VE hypervisor cluster for Kubernetes infrastructure and application VMs
      </p>
      <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
        <strong>Cluster Status:</strong> 3-host cluster with mixed Proxmox versions | 
        <strong>Container Orchestration:</strong> Kubernetes with Flannel CNI (3+ nodes) |
        <strong>Primary Database:</strong> Bare-metal at 192.168.1.198 (outside Proxmox)
      </p>
      
