        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">172.30.161.222</td>
          <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">zthnhd6k65</td>
          <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Remote Cooperative Node</td>
          <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">External Network</td>
          <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">coop.local (offsite VPN mesh)</td>
          <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><a href="[% c.uri_for('/Documentation/system/Server_Room_IP_Registry') %]" style="color: var(--link-color);">IP_Registry:358</a></td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">5.2 Verification & Troubleshooting</h3>
      <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">To verify ZeroTier connectivity from any K8s node:</p>
      <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
        <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0;"><code>
# List all connected ZeroTier networks
zerotier-cli listnetworks

# Ping K8s master from worker (using ZeroTier IP)
ping 172.30.204.11

# Check inter-node communication
kubectl get nodes -o wide   # View all node ZeroTier IPs

# Verify K8s services can reach database
kubectl run --rm -it --image=busybox busybox -- \
  wget -O- http://172.30.204.11:443  # K8s API endpoint
        </code></pre>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: #c8e6c9; border-left: 4px solid #388e3c; padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-medium) 0;">
        <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin: 0;"><strong>✅ ZeroTier Status:</strong> All K8s nodes successfully connected to ZeroTier mesh. This network replaces the previous 192.168.123.x bridge and provides secure, encrypted inter-node communication. See <a href="[% c.uri_for('/Documentation/system/PRODUCTION_DB_KUBERNETES_MIGRATION_PLAN') %]" style="color: var(--link-color);">PRODUCTION_DB_KUBERNETES_MIGRATION_PLAN.tt:1390</a> for setup verification commands.</p>
      </div>

      <p style="text-align: right; margin-top: var(--spacing-small);"><a href="#toc" style="color: var(--link-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">↑ Back to Top</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>

